<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="weep-vi">weep <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /wiːp/    美 /wiːp/  </p>
<p>(wept, wept)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>流泪；哭泣：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>weep for joy</strong>
喜极而泣</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When Claire got home, she <strong>wept with</strong> anger in her armchair.
回家后，克莱尔气得坐在椅子上哭了起来。</p><footer>人教⑦ – 2</footer></div></div>